Add elf-related definitions for LoongArch, including: EM_LOONGARCH,
KEXEC_ARCH_LOONGARCH, AUDIT_ARCH_LOONGARCH32, AUDIT_ARCH_LOONGARCH64
and NT_LOONGARCH_*.

